tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE protein_interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  protein1_id INT NOT NULL,
  protein2_id INT NOT NULL,
  interaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (protein1_id) REFERENCES proteins(protein_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (protein2_id) REFERENCES proteins(protein_id)
);

CREATE TABLE ProteinInteractions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein1_id INT,
    protein2_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_score DECIMAL(10,2)
);

CREATE TABLE Proteins (
    protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_name VARCHAR(255),
    gene_name VARCHAR(255),
    organism VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE Interactions (
    interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein1_id INT,
    protein2_id INT,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Pathways (
    pathway_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    pathway_name VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE PathwayProteins (
    pathway_id INT,
    protein_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE ExperimentResults (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    experiment_type VARCHAR(50),
    protein_id INT,
    pathway_id INT,
    result_data TEXT
)
